{
  "stem": "17308.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 399.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't-- it wasn't a big area, and it was no industry there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was no business area mainly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then, it returned to tranquility after they left-- typical country area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wouldn't say that the population was pro-German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wouldn't say that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were very anti German, but not in, like, some area where they had what they call a lot of collaborators.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was, I would say, a-- I would say that more than 99% was anti-German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were always hoping, of course, Germany will get defeated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was a very minor part.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, just assisting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was paperwork, moving items like-- mainly paperwork.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, not office.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there were people coming around, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to hand over documentation and things like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well, I didn't read it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was documentation about movement, of German movement, things happening in the area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they had-- in the mountains, there was quite a strong group of the Resistance, the Maquis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "M-A-Q-U-I-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was sabotage, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were mining railways, bridges.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we were not allowed to listen to the radio.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was what we called the de Gaulle movement, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had the regular broadcast to France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's when they used to play that famous tune from Beethoven, The Fifth Symphony.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was the opening tune.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the beginning, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But afterwards, when we heard the radio, we knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew-- at the first stage, we didn't know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody was aware.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But coming from England, the news were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was about '42.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, it started early '42, you know, that we knew exactly-- not exactly.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
